{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417800/extras/Key_Art_RevisedWIP-15.png?t=1737165787\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417800/extras/Gif2.gif?t=1737165787\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight and lead your army from a ground level view of large fantasy battles, command your formation of troops, and direct your forces through hack-and-slash encounters to claim ultimate victory! Go head to head in objective based conquest mode, or test your defensive skills in a wave based survival mode. Varied troop types offer distinct fighting styles and weapons, allowing for diverse playstyles and tactics. Will you anchor a battle line with spearmen, shatter defenses with mighty great swords, or rain arrows upon your enemies?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417800/extras/Key_Art_RevisedWIP-14.png?t=1737165787\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417800/extras/Gif1.gif?t=1737165787\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Included in this demo are the following features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Tutorial missions explaining basic mechanics and main game modes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Human and Undead playable factions (Elves, Orcs, and Dwarves included in full game)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">2 Conquest Maps against either bots or other players in couch coop</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">1 wave survival Siege Mode Map.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackgroun