ords, or rain arrows upon your enemies?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417800/extras/Key_Art_RevisedWIP-14.png?t=1737165787\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417800/extras/Gif1.gif?t=1737165787\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Included in this demo are the following features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Tutorial missions explaining basic mechanics and main game modes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Human and Undead playable factions (Elves, Orcs, and Dwarves included in full game)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">2 Conquest Maps against either bots or other players in couch coop</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">1 wave survival Siege Mode Map.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","developers":["Refractal Studio"],"fullgame":{"appid":"2581120","name":"Broad Sword"},"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Simulation","id":"28"},{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417800/header.jpg?t=1737165787","is_free":true,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257083551,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257083551/movie480.mp4?t=1736704412","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257083551/movie_max.mp4?t=1736704412"},"name":"Broad Sword Gameplay Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257083551/f9324e31b0ba8ae2141e2a9495750da9d31a8eb1/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1736704412","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257083551/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1736704412","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257